			<div class="content" id="post-content-1831502">
									

<p>Well, since it's summer&#8230; requests are still open! No idea when I'll get around to them, but I have more time now than I did before. My only request is that if you're going to ask for a villanelle, it should be for an SCP you've written, and if possible, not rated too highly. I like using this to draw attention to less-viewed articles. ;)</p>
